OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fscattered showers will clear this
OL,7,Fevening. The rest of the night will
OL,8,Fthen be dry with clear spells, though
OL,9,Fsome mist and fog may affect northern
OL,10,Fcoastal areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FDry and settled with light
OL,13,Fwinds. Fairly cloudy at first, but
OL,14,Fbrightening up with some good spells
OL,15,Fof warm sunshine for the rest of the
OL,16,Fday. Warm in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
